WEBVTT

00:06:58.040 --> 00:07:01.080
If life in your village
weren't so precarious,

00:07:02.440 --> 00:07:05.816
if there was a way
to having enough food to get by,

00:07:05.840 --> 00:07:07.320
or having a paying job --

00:07:08.800 --> 00:07:10.136
if you and your sisters

00:07:10.160 --> 00:07:15.496
didn't have to spend
30 percent of their waking hours

00:07:15.520 --> 00:07:16.840
fetching water,

00:07:18.240 --> 00:07:20.880
if conditions were just
a little more hospitable ...

00:07:23.800 --> 00:07:26.800
could the solution
be right here in our soil?

00:07:28.280 --> 00:07:31.176
Could bringing fonio
to the rest of the world